videos.description: Texas A&M's Robert Williams takes the pass from Chris Collins and elevates for the jam.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Williams impresses early with emphatic dunk

videos.description: West Virginia's Teyvon Myers goes behind the back before finding an opening for the lay-in.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Myers uses behind-the-back dribble to score

videos.description: West Virginia is beginning to pour it on after Brandon Watkins' layup keeps West Virginia up by double digits.
videos.headline: West Virginia finding groove at end of first half

videos.description: Brandon Watkins  hits the jumper and gets fouled in the process, as West Virginia continues to look sharp vs. Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Watkins hits jumper and draws foul for West Virginia

videos.description: Daxter Miles Jr. gets the steal and easy bucket, as West Virginia looks to close the game out vs. Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Steal leads to easy West Virginia bucket

videos.description: West Virginia's Jevon Carter talks about the hard-fought win over Texas A&M.
videos.headline: West Virginia's Jevon Carter breaks down win over Texas A&M
